ars-worth.html</a></div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51438483">3 Likes </b> <b id='shb51438483'></b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51438519"></a><a name="msg51438519"></a><a name="3489685.21"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51438519">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/kingdenny" class=user title="Location: lagos Nigeria">kingdenny</a>(<span class="m">m</span>): <span class=s><b>5:35am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51438519" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>In politics, the main drama is behind the scene<br>not what we see on tv and newspapers. <br>Buhari is never a saint , i wonder the amount of skeletons he has stashed up in his closet.<br>I wish something like rapture can catch up with all our old politicians or earth quake to swallow them up.<br>This is what is holding us back as a nation</div><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51438865"></a><a name="msg51438865"></a><a name="3489685.22"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51438865">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/rose54321" class=user>rose54321</a>: <span class=s><b>6:15am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51438865" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Hmm. Tell us what we don't know. <br><br>Hopefully Inec can capitalize on the card reader so that 2019 ..</div><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51439073"></a><a name="msg51439073"></a><a name="3489685.23"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51439073">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/veekid" class=user title="Location: Ibadan">veekid</a>(<span class="m">m</span>): <span class=s><b>6:30am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51439073" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>There's hunger on the land</div><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51439620"></a><a name="msg51439620"></a><a name="3489685.24"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51439620">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/paperwhite" class=user>Paperwhite</a>(<span class="m">m</span>): <span class=s><b>7:02am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51439620" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Guess the centre can't hold again? The broom is now scattered.</div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51439620">4 Likes </b> <b id='shb51439620'> 1 Share</b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51440102"></a><a name="msg51440102"></a><a name="3489685.25"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51440102">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/sekundosekundo" class=user title="Location: SHARJAH ">sekundosekundo</a>: <span class=s><b>7:27am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51440102" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Buhari is like Nigerian prisons when one is put in there, he'll come out worst. In the name of fighting corruption, Buhari have introduced grave corruption in the land.</div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51440102">2 Likes </b> <b id='shb51440102'></b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51440125"></a><a name="msg51440125"></a><a name="3489685.26"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51440125">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/kings09" class=user title="Location: Lagos">kings09</a>(<span class="m">m</span>): <span class=s><b>7:28am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51440125" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Buba Galadima is an Ipod - zombies . <br><br>Sarrki, rusher14, madridguy, kyase, progressive01 oya e gbera</div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51440125">6 Likes </b> <b id='shb51440125'></b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51440172"></a><a name="msg51440172"></a><a name="3489685.27"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51440172">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/delgardo" class=user>DelGardo</a>: <span class=s><b>7:30am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51440172" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>You guys can wail all you like. Buhari I on the right track after 16 years of destructive politics and cluelessness. There is no more free money, and reckless stealing will be punished. <br><br>Get up on your lazy behinds, pull out from MMM, stop playing bets and think! Otherwise <b>aguu g'egbukwa unu</b> <img src="http://www.nairaland.com/faces/grin.png" alt="grin" border="0" class="faces">. <br><br>The Nigeria of tomorrow depends on those who can create value not the importers of fake Chinese products.</div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51440172">2 Likes </b> <b id='shb51440172'></b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51440527"></a><a name="msg51440527"></a><a name="3489685.28"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51440527">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/stalwert" class=user>Stalwert</a>: <span class=s><b>7:44am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51440527" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Sir you made your decision live with it and stop your subterranean campaign for atiku</div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51440527">1 Like </b> <b id='shb51440527'></b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51440536"></a><a name="msg51440536"></a><a name="3489685.29"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51440536">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/izonpikin" class=user>Izonpikin</a>: <span class=s><b>7:44am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51440536" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Where is bashydemy<img src="/faces/huh.png" style="width:15px;height:22px;"><br><br>Come and dance around your God buhari..buhari remains a failure .A stubborn one at that..</div><p class=s> <b id="lpt51440536">2 Likes </b> <b id='shb51440536'></b><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51440848"></a><a name="msg51440848"></a><a name="3489685.30"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51440848">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/abuayman" class=user title="Location: Abuja">abuayman</a>(<span class="m">m</span>): <span class=s><b>7:56am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51440848" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow>Bubu Galadima</div><tr><td class="bold l pu"><a name="51441149"></a><a name="msg51441149"></a><a name="3489685.31"></a><a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing#51441149">Re: Under Buhari, People Are Just Stealing Left, Right And Centre —buba Galadima</a> by <a href="/bashydemy" class=user title="Location: COTONOU">bashydemy</a>(<span class="m">m</span>): <span class=s><b>8:07am</b></span><tr><td id="pb51441149" class="l w pd"><div class=narrow><blockquote><a href=/post/51440536><b>Izonpikin</a></b>:<br>Where is bashydemy<img src="/faces/huh.png" style="width:15px;height:22px;"><br><br>Come and dance around your God buhari..buhari remains a failure .A stubborn one at that..</blockquote><br><br><br>LOL what this? i dint see anything here other ranting up and down.</div></table><div class=nocopy><p><b>(0)</b> <a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing/1">(1)</a> <a href="/3489685/under-buhari-people-just-stealing/2">(2)</a> (<a href="http://www.nairaland.com/newpost?topic=3489685"><b>Reply</b></a>) <div class=moneyz><a href="/click/politics/111" rel=nofollow><img src="http://www.nairaland.com/moneyz/ujsti16vmkvlxuxyzafqz3hlbs1j0np6.png"></a><a href="/click/politics/2708" rel=nofollow><img src="http://www.nairaland.com/moneyz/0k3llun0ztigkfwmx8lk7eezrtqzbdra.jpg"></a><a href="/click/politics/4947" rel=nofollow><img src="http://www.nairaland.com/moneyz/wpyxil0mzg869f0275tssjwnokckk2js.jpg"></a></div><p> <a href="/2907537/women-delegates-visit-aisha-buhari">Women Delegates Visit Aisha Buhari In Her Home (Photos)</a> / <a href="/3467490/okorocha-campaigning-akeredolu-aketi-akure">Okorocha Campaigning For Akeredolu Aketi In Akure (Photos)</a> / <a href="/2059119/buhari-gets-44.5